  "title": "C&S Design Engineer / MRT Tunnel/ Upto $7.5k basic+Vb/5day/A1 maincon MNC",
  "description": "<ul><li><ul><li><p><strong>Up to Basic $7.5k + Variable Bonus!</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Permanent position/ 5 workdays</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Participate in MRT Tunnel project in the Bukit Timah area.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Experience in MRT Tunnel projects is mandatory. </strong></p></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>Our client is a reputable MNC and leading A1 main contractor diverse in civil and infrastructure project.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Coordination of civil/structural works for construction</p></li><li><p>Liaise and coordinate with other stakeholders and consultants on the design and technical issues relating to temporary works.</p></li><li><p>Attend meetings with Client, subcontractors and consultants.</p></li><li><p>Liaise closely with internal and external parties include consultant, relevant authorities agencies to resolve structural design discrepancies, updates and submissions of project design.  </p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/Degree in Civil Engineering or its equivalent</p></li><li><p>Experience in <strong>MRT Tunnel projects </strong>is mandatory. </p></li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW button or email your resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">search84@searchindex.com.sg</a><strong> with the following detail:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Reason for leaving each past & current employment</p></li><li><p>Salary drawn for each past & current employment</p></li><li><p>Expected Salary</p></li><li><p>Earliest availability date</p></li></ul><p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong></p><p><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
